		<!-- <Section title='About'> -->
			<p class='text-muted-foreground'>
				I am a PhD student at Ruhr University Bochum in cooperation with Hochschule Bonn-Rhein-Sieg, Germany.
        I am also a research associate at the Institute for AI and Autonomous Systems, Hochschule Bonn-Rhein-Sieg since 2020.
				I obtained my master's degree in Autonomous Systems from Hochschule Bonn-Rhein-Sieg and 
        my research interests include continual or lifelong learning for embodied autonomous systems and robotics.
